cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DS, cs.RO, cs.NE 

The paper discusses the use of reinforcement learning algorithms with deep neural networks and tree search for combinatorial optimization problems. This falls under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), robotics (cs.RO), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE). However, since the paper focuses on the use of reinforcement learning, cs.LG and cs.AI are the most likely categories.
